0.1.1

Forked from http://sourceforge.net/projects/bpm/ trying to find author "pat03".

0.1:
  * Added the abilty to have command line args.
  * Removed the check for the bpm group, will be re-added later.
	* Added help and usage messages.
	* Added clean up function if SIGHUP, SIGINT or SIGTERM signals are received.
  * Coloured output is here :D
  * Added --info, --verbose, --ask, --help arguments.
  * Added an error function to handle errors in a clean way.
  * Added a debug function
	* And lots more :)

